<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Product Landing Page</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/landingpageStyles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar">
            <div class="navbar-brand">
                <a href="/home"> <span class = 'withinlogo'>eco</span>Sense</a>
            </div>
            <ul class="navbar-nav">
                <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Order Now</a></li>
                <li class="navbar-btn"><a href="/login">Login to Console</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Meet EcoSense</h1>
            <p>Your ultimate solution for environmental monitoring</p>
            <a href="#features" class="btn" id = 'learnbutton'>Watch a demo</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image">
            <img src="/images/whitepcb.png" alt="Product Image">
        </div>
    </section>


    <section id="features" class="features">
        <h2>Included Features</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-item">
                <img class = 'featureimage' src="/images/featurephoto_2.png" alt="Product Image">
                <h3>Real-Time Data</h3>
                <p>Get accurate, up-to-the-minute data on temperature, humidity, and light levels.</p>
            </div>
           
            <div class="feature-item">
                <img src="/images/featurephoto_1.png" alt="Product Image">
                <h3>High-Quality Visualizations</h3>
                <p>Visualize your data with customizable, dynamic charts and graphs.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
                <img src="/images/featurephoto_3.png" alt="Product Image">
                <h3>Data Storage</h3>
                <p>Store your environmental data securely and access it anytime.</p>
            </div>



            <div class="feature-item">
                <img src="/images/featurephoto_4.png" alt="Product Image">
                <h3>Fully Customizable Alerts</h3>
                <p>Recieve instant text notifications based on custom alerts to inform the state of the sensor.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
                <img src="/images/featurephoto_5.png" alt="Product Image">
                <h3>In-App Custom Sensor Calibration</h3>
                <p>While our sensors are shipped calibrated, we offer full control for user created calibrations.</p>
            </div>


            <div class="feature-item">
                <img src="/images/featurephoto_6.png" alt="Product Image">
                <h3>CSV Data Download</h3>
                <p>Complete access to download raw sensor data in CSV format, allowing for further analysis or proccessing.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="about">
        <div class="about-content">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>
                At ecoSense, we are committed to delivering precise and reliable environmental monitoring solutions. 
                Our innovative products ensure accurate data and high-quality visualizations. We prioritize customer 
                satisfaction through exceptional service and support, 
                providing the best user experience in the industry. Trust SensorPro for your environmental monitoring needs.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image">
            <img src="/images/background_x.jpg" alt="Product Image">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="contact">
        <h2>Contact our Team</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or need more information, feel free to reach out to us!</p>
        <form action="/contact" method="post">
            <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
            <textarea name="message" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
            <button type="submit" class="btn">Send Message</button>
        </form>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 ecoSense. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
